LOCUS       Bst-LF_pTI              6971 bp ds-DNA     circular     10-FEB-2026
DEFINITION  .
COMMENT     BstLF expression under pT7_Lac0 promoter (i.e. It has a Lac0 box to
            improve the promoter repression).  This system drives the
            expression of BstLF in the presence of RNAT7 polymerase (which
            typically is induced by IPTG in E.coli BL21).
            pT7_Lac0::Riboj54_B0034_His_tag::GS_linker::BstLF::3xStop::Tz in
            pTI_O1 Kanamycin Resistant LacI translation rate from 4valine :
            2275.31 accord to RBS calculator. Primers for sequencing: BST_F1:
            TGTTGTGTTCGACCTGCTGCTG BST_F2: GCGTGTTCTTGCTCACATTGCG
            BST_R2:CGCACGTTGAAGTTACGGGAGG
